### FutureOfWork AI API - Exemplos de Requisições
### Para usar este arquivo, instale a extensão REST Client no VS Code

@baseUrl = https://localhost:7000
@apiKey = FutureOfWork-API-Key-2024

### 1. Health Check (sem autenticação)
GET {{baseUrl}}/health
Accept: application/json

###

### 2. Informações da API (sem autenticação)
GET {{baseUrl}}/
Accept: application/json

###

### 3. Listar Modelos Disponíveis
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/ai/models
Accept: application/json
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

###

### 4. OCR de Currículo (PDF)
# Nota: Para testar no VS Code REST Client, substitua o caminho do arquivo
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/ai/ocr-resume
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="cv.pdf"
Content-Type: application/pdf

< ./caminho/para/seu/cv.pdf
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

###

### 5. OCR de Currículo (Imagem PNG)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/ai/ocr-resume
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="cv.png"
Content-Type: image/png

< ./caminho/para/seu/cv.png
